<font face="Serif" size="18">When the Night-Family activates,
blend in.</font>

176
00:10:12,529 --> 00:10:15,865
<font face="Serif" size="18">Make them think you're Night-Summer.
If you start to nod off, suck on this tube.</font>

177
00:10:15,949 --> 00:10:16,783
<font face="Serif" size="18">What is it?</font>

178
00:10:16,866 --> 00:10:18,576
<font face="Serif" size="18">A cocktail of Mountain Dew
and DayQuil.</font>

179
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:20,495
<font face="Serif" size="18">The kids in Southern Europe
call it DewQuil.</font>

180
00:10:20,578 --> 00:10:21,871
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Smells gross.
- It is.</font>

181
00:10:21,955 --> 00:10:24,999
<font face="Serif" size="18">Once you find the Somnambulator,
use this deactivator Puck.</font>

182
00:10:25,083 --> 00:10:28,503
<font face="Serif" size="18">Stick it on the Somnambulator.
When the puck activates, it'll fry its circuits.</font>

183
00:10:29,295 --> 00:10:33,133
<font face="Serif" size="18">Remember: Stay awake. All night.
Meet me back here at sunrise.</font>

184
00:10:34,259 --> 00:10:35,385
<font face="Serif" size="18">[sighs]</font>

185
00:10:56,781 --> 00:10:58,074
<font face="Serif" size="18">[keypad beeping]</font>

186
00:11:24,017 --> 00:11:27,437
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why are you wearing that suit?</font>

187
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:29,105
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yeah, why?
- Yes.</font>

188
00:11:32,525 --> 00:11:33,818
<font face="Serif" size="18">Yeah.</font>

189
00:11:33,902 --> 00:11:37,655
<font face="Serif" size="18">Because
you're all such clothing experts.</font>

190
00:11:38,323 --> 00:11:39,866
<font face="Serif" size="18">That's fair.</font>

191
00:11:39,949 --> 00:11:41,784
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Fair enough.
- Point taken.</font>

192
00:11:41,868 --> 00:11:45,079
<font face="Serif" size="18">Get back to work.</font>

193
00:11:45,163 --> 00:11:49,167
<font face="Serif" size="18">I rule the night and stuff.</font>

194
00:11:49,250 --> 00:11:50,251
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yes.
- Okay.</font>

195
00:11:50,335 --> 00:11:51,961
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Will do.
- As you wish.</font>

196
00:11:53,338 --> 00:11:54,756
<font face="Serif" size="18">[beeping rapidly]</font>

197
00:11:56,466 --> 00:11:58,051
<font face="Serif" size="18">Grandpa Rick! Rick, wake up!</font>

198
00:11:58,134 --> 00:12:00,303
<font face="Serif" size="18">What? I'm up! I'm up!
Did you find it?</font>

199
00:12:00,386 --> 00:12:03,264
<font face="Serif" size="18">For sure. You were souping up
the Somnambu-whatever</font>

200
00:12:03,348 --> 00:12:05,934
<font face="Serif" size="18">so they could extend
its range beyond the house.</font>

201
00:12:06,017 --> 00:12:10,188
<font face="Serif" size="18">But I defeated that shit when
I put the thing on top of the thing.</font>

202
00:12:10,271 --> 00:12:12,941
<font face="Serif" size="18">Everybody, wake up!
Summer fried the Somnambulator!</font>

203
00:12:13,024 --> 00:12:16,110
<font face="Serif" size="18">- The nightmare is over!
- Really? Oh! That's amazing!</font>

204
00:12:16,194 --> 00:12:19,989
<font face="Serif" size="18">Almost got pinched but yeah,
say adiós to the Night-Family.</font>

205
00:12:20,073 --> 00:12:21,199
<font face="Serif" size="18">Bye-bye, pen pal.</font>

206
00:12:22,033 --> 00:12:25,078
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I want Shoney's pancakes!
- Yes! Shoney's pancakes!</font>

207
00:12:25,161 --> 00:12:27,121
<font face="Serif" size="18">All right, brunch is on me,
Day-Family.</font>

208
00:12:29,582 --> 00:12:32,043
<font face="Serif" size="18">For a second there, I thought
Night-Summer was gonna win.</font>

209
00:12:32,126 --> 00:12:35,088
<font face="Serif" size="18">- That chick is the absolute worst.
- Sorry, Rick.</font>

210
00:12:35,171 --> 00:12:38,633
<font face="Serif" size="18">But your opinion
means very little to me.</font>

211
00:12:38,716 --> 00:12:44,222
<font face="Serif" size="18">Did you think you could
stop me with this, Rick?</font>

212
00:12:45,014 --> 00:12:46,808
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone 1] Halt, Day-manoids!</font>

213
00:12:46,891 --> 00:12:48,309
<font face="Serif" size="18">Everyone! Get behind my abs!</font>

214
00:12:48,393 --> 00:12:52,021
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone 2] Do not move! Do not move!</font>

215
00:12:52,105 --> 00:12:54,065
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone 3] You are most definitely surrounded.</font>

216
00:12:54,148 --> 00:12:58,403
<font face="Serif" size="18">You are the slaves now.</font>

217
00:12:58,486 --> 00:13:05,118
<font face="Serif" size="18">If you have any doubt,
I suggest you sleep on it.</font>

218
00:13:05,201 --> 00:13:07,370
<font face="Serif" size="18">- She's Night-Summer!
- Thanks, Jerry.</font>

219
00:13:13,835 --> 00:13:18,172
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone 1] Work! Work! The function
of the Day-manoid is to serve the night.</font>

220
00:13:18,256 --> 00:13:20,550
<font face="Serif" size="18">Work harder! Harder!</font>

221
00:13:20,633 --> 00:13:25,054
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>It is natural for the day
to serve the night.</i></font>

222
00:13:25,138 --> 00:13:31,853
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>Night was here long before day.
Half of all time is night time.</i></font>

223
00:13:31,936 --> 00:13:35,606
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone 2] 157, 158...</font>

224
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:38,359
<font face="Serif" size="18">- One hundred and--
- No more, please! I hate exercise!</font>

225
00:13:38,443 --> 00:13:41,195
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone 2] Silence! Crunch harder! Harder!</font>

226
00:13:41,279 --> 00:13:43,573
<font face="Serif" size="18">We have to escape
the Somnambulator's reach.</font>

227
00:13:43,656 --> 00:13:45,783
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Do we even know how far that is?
- No.</font>

228
00:13:45,867 --> 00:13:48,911
<font face="Serif" size="18">Cards on the table, we may be
really eff-ed in the A this time.</font>

229
00:13:49,579 --> 00:13:53,124
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone 3] Report to your designated
sleep pod for rest period.</font>

230
00:14:15,521 --> 00:14:19,650
<font face="Serif" size="18">[whispering] I'm a friend of your son-in-law.
Come with me.</font>

231
00:14:19,734 --> 00:14:20,568
<font face="Serif" size="18">- What?
- How?</font>

232
00:14:20,651 --> 00:14:24,864
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hurry. We don't have long before
the Proxy-drones go back online.</font>

233
00:14:28,201 --> 00:14:29,494
<font face="Serif" size="18">Thank you, Night-Jerry.</font>

234
00:14:29,577 --> 00:14:34,207
<font face="Serif" size="18">Anything to help Day-Jerry's family.
He's a very special per so--</font>

235
00:14:34,874 --> 00:14:36,542
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hey! Ow! Why?</font>

236
00:14:36,626 --> 00:14:39,629
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Nice. You got our Jerry back.
- Uh, yeah. Totally why I did that.</font>

237
00:14:39,712 --> 00:14:41,756
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Everybody in Rick's car!
- Morty! Wait!</font>

238
00:14:44,801 --> 00:14:46,677
<font face="Serif" size="18">Having a bit of trouble with your car?</font>

239
00:14:46,761 --> 00:14:49,305
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Rick] Not now, Gene!
- [drone 1] Day-manoids are restricted</font>

240
00:14:49,389 --> 00:14:51,057
<font face="Serif" size="18">from the outside world!</font>

241
00:14:51,724 --> 00:14:53,476
<font face="Serif" size="18">Halt! Halt!</font>

242
00:14:53,559 --> 00:14:54,644
<font face="Serif" size="18">Hold on to your tits.</font>

243
00:14:55,728 --> 00:14:57,313
<font face="Serif" size="18">[tires screeching]</font>

244
00:14:59,273 --> 00:15:00,733
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Where am I going?
- To the airport!</font>

245
00:15:00,817 --> 00:15:02,819
<font face="Serif" size="18">We have to get far away
from the Somnambulator</font>

246
00:15:02,902 --> 00:15:04,028
<font face="Serif" size="18">before we fall asleep.</font>

247
00:15:04,112 --> 00:15:06,155
<font face="Serif" size="18">What about Summer?
We can't leave her behind.</font>

248
00:15:06,239 --> 00:15:09,367
<font face="Serif" size="18">She's not your sister anymore.
Consider her dead. Eat shit, Summer!</font>

249
00:15:09,450 --> 00:15:10,952
<font face="Serif" size="18">You gotta shake those robots.</font>

250
00:15:19,001 --> 00:15:20,336
<font face="Serif" size="18">I think we lost 'em!</font>

251
00:15:22,004 --> 00:15:23,548
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Beth] Son of a bitch!</font>

252
00:15:25,967 --> 00:15:27,510
<font face="Serif" size="18">[Rick] Damn it, we lost Morty!</font>

253
00:15:29,804 --> 00:15:31,139
<font face="Serif" size="18">Beth! Watch out!</font>

254
00:15:31,222 --> 00:15:33,641
<font face="Serif" size="18">You cannot escape-- Ah! Shit!</font>

255
00:15:40,022 --> 00:15:41,065
<font face="Serif" size="18">Huh?</font>

256
00:15:41,858 --> 00:15:44,193
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [siren wailing]
- Stop or I'll shoot everyone!</font>

257
00:15:52,285 --> 00:15:56,789
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Take the wheel.
- As you wish.</font>

258
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:01,294
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let go of me, you little shit!</font>

259
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:10,928
<font face="Serif" size="18">- No! You're going the wrong way!
- Silence, Day-breather!</font>

260
00:16:11,012 --> 00:16:13,639
<font face="Serif" size="18">- [Jerry] Morty, you're choking me.
- I know!</font>

261
00:16:14,974 --> 00:16:16,184
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ow. What the heck, Dad?</font>

262
00:16:17,393 --> 00:16:18,853
<font face="Serif" size="18">[truck horn honking]</font>

263
00:16:20,646 --> 00:16:21,939
<font face="Serif" size="18">Help me stop your mom!</font>

264
00:16:23,941 --> 00:16:26,360
<font face="Serif" size="18">Look out, you useless old man.</font>

265
00:16:27,570 --> 00:16:28,779
<font face="Serif" size="18">What the hell?</font>

266
00:16:28,863 --> 00:16:31,908
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Give me that gun and take the wheel, stupid.
- Jesus! Sorry!</font>

267
00:16:38,247 --> 00:16:39,499
<font face="Serif" size="18">[shouting]</font>

268
00:16:44,921 --> 00:16:45,796
<font face="Serif" size="18">Ugh.</font>

269
00:16:47,798 --> 00:16:49,133
<font face="Serif" size="18">[screams]</font>

270
00:16:49,217 --> 00:16:52,553
<font face="Serif" size="18">The Night-Family's trying to make us go home!
You gotta turn around!</font>

271
00:16:57,266 --> 00:16:58,851
<font face="Serif" size="18">Why even bother, Gene?</font>

272
00:17:00,853 --> 00:17:04,106
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Good job, Mom. Back on course.
- Almost didn't make it.</font>

273
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:06,400
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone] Hit the sheets, Day-manoids.</font>

274
00:17:08,194 --> 00:17:11,239
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Night-Person!
- Hey! I'm on your side!</font>

275
00:17:11,322 --> 00:17:13,157
<font face="Serif" size="18">- I'm on your side!
- Oh, that's right.</font>

276
00:17:13,241 --> 00:17:14,158
<font face="Serif" size="18">Sorry! Rough day.</font>

277
00:17:14,242 --> 00:17:15,535
<font face="Serif" size="18">[drone] Day-manoids.</font>

278
00:17:19,080 --> 00:17:20,039
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fla-Hoigan!</font>

279
00:17:23,584 --> 00:17:25,419
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Come on! Jump!
- Why?</font>

280
00:17:25,503 --> 00:17:28,256
<font face="Serif" size="18">I'm already in
a perfectly functional car!</font>

281
00:17:28,339 --> 00:17:30,341
<font face="Serif" size="18">Uh... family?</font>

282
00:17:30,424 --> 00:17:31,509
<font face="Serif" size="18">Aw.</font>

283
00:17:43,229 --> 00:17:45,273
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Everybody awake?
- Ow!</font>

284
00:17:45,356 --> 00:17:46,941
<font face="Serif" size="18">- We are now.
- Hey, what the hay?</font>

285
00:17:48,693 --> 00:17:51,779
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Looks like we're gonna make it, kids.
- Ow.</font>

286
00:17:52,863 --> 00:17:55,783
<font face="Serif" size="18">Nighty-night, slaves.</font>

287
00:17:55,866 --> 00:17:56,701
<font face="Serif" size="18">Fuck.</font>

288
00:17:56,784 --> 00:17:57,994
<font face="Serif" size="18">[tires screeching]</font>

289
00:18:04,792 --> 00:18:05,626
<font face="Serif" size="18">Take that!</font>

290
00:18:13,968 --> 00:18:14,802
<font face="Serif" size="18">Take that!</font>

291
00:18:15,553 --> 00:18:17,013
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Hold him down.
- No! No!</font>

292
00:18:18,139 --> 00:18:21,976
<font face="Serif" size="18">[whispering] Stop! Rick, we're all the same people.</font>

293
00:18:22,059 --> 00:18:23,894
<font face="Serif" size="18">There must be some agreement</font>

294
00:18:23,978 --> 00:18:27,523
<font face="Serif" size="18">we can reach to stop
this god-awful conflict?</font>

295
00:18:27,607 --> 00:18:28,899
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, like what?</font>

296
00:18:28,983 --> 00:18:31,444
<font face="Serif" size="18">I would consider a truce,</font>

297
00:18:31,527 --> 00:18:35,323
<font face="Serif" size="18">if the Day-manoids
would rinse their dishes.</font>

298
00:18:35,406 --> 00:18:37,700
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Yes, rinse!
- Fine by me.</font>

299
00:18:37,783 --> 00:18:39,285
<font face="Serif" size="18">That seems fair.</font>

300
00:18:39,368 --> 00:18:44,790
<font face="Serif" size="18">We can end all of this right now
if you agree to rinse your dishes.</font>

301
00:18:44,874 --> 00:18:46,709
<font face="Serif" size="18">What do you say, Rick?</font>

302
00:18:53,883 --> 00:18:57,303
<font face="Serif" size="18">Let's go home. Right, Grandpa?</font>

303
00:18:57,386 --> 00:18:59,472
<font face="Serif" size="18">Great idea, Summer.</font>

304
00:19:00,681 --> 00:19:01,974
<font face="Serif" size="18">[soft rock music playing]</font>

305
00:19:37,885 --> 00:19:41,055
<font face="Serif" size="18">[man] <i>So until you pay that fee,
plus the multiple overdue charges,</i></font>

306
00:19:41,138 --> 00:19:42,515
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>your account will remain frozen.</i></font>

307
00:19:42,598 --> 00:19:46,268
<font face="Serif" size="18">Normally this would have been dealt
with by our Day-manoid oppressors</font>

308
00:19:46,352 --> 00:19:49,605
<font face="Serif" size="18">but we recently freed ourselves
from the shackles of the night.</font>

309
00:19:49,689 --> 00:19:51,482
<font face="Serif" size="18"><i>I got 30 more calls to make today.</i></font>

310
00:19:52,024 --> 00:19:54,610
<font face="Serif" size="18">The bank repossessed the car.</font>

311
00:19:54,694 --> 00:19:56,195
<font face="Serif" size="18">Aw, man.</font>

312
00:19:56,278 --> 00:20:00,199
<font face="Serif" size="18">I got logged out of my Twitter account
and don't know my password. Shit.</font>

313
00:20:00,282 --> 00:20:03,160
<font face="Serif" size="18">We spent all the Day-people's money
on vacations,</font>

314
00:20:03,244 --> 00:20:07,832
<font face="Serif" size="18">renting concert halls and night-centric
streaming subscriptions.</font>

315
00:20:07,915 --> 00:20:08,874
<font face="Serif" size="18">We're broke.</font>

316
00:20:08,958 --> 00:20:12,712
<font face="Serif" size="18">I guess, there's a lot more work
to seizing the day than I thought.</font>

317
00:20:13,629 --> 00:20:14,922
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all groaning]</font>

318
00:20:15,005 --> 00:20:20,594
<font face="Serif" size="18">I have a device that
will solve all of our problems.</font>

319
00:20:31,856 --> 00:20:35,526
<font face="Serif" size="18">- Whoa. How long have we been asleep?
- Can't be that long.</font>

320
00:20:36,318 --> 00:20:39,697
<font face="Serif" size="18">Oh, my God! No!
They killed the choco taco!</font>

321
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:41,031
<font face="Serif" size="18">[all screaming]</font>

